				<td colspan="2"><span>If any of you have been to Nedaria's Landing yet, it looks cool.  And since I am very much into LDoN, I am eagerly awaiting what adventures err explorations those ships will take us on.<img src="/skins/default/images/emotions/emotion-1.gif" border="0" alt="Smiley" hspace="2" />
<br />

<br />
Information on augment types:  If you look at your items, you can see what type of augments it will take.  Your standard gear will take up to type 7.  That means all the type 1 augments that drop in the LDoN addys can be augmented onto your normal items.  Elemental Planes armor can take type 8 I believe.  Most weapons I think go up to type 4.  Not sure about that.</span></td>
